    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307610/extras/1f9b4d4545a8eab3f394d55116c52b5f.poster.avif?t=1768507899\" width=800 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307610/extras/1f9b4d4545a8eab3f394d55116c52b5f.webm?t=1768507899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307610/extras/1f9b4d4545a8eab3f394d55116c52b5f.mp4?t=1768507899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到 <strong>Ultimate Golf Battle</strong> — 经典迷你高尔夫的混乱多人对战版本！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原本轻松的比赛很快就会变成全面混乱，当强化道具、物理效果与纯粹技巧碰撞时，你将体验前所未有的乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌握棘手的球场，智胜你的朋友，证明精准与混乱也能在球场上共存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307610/extras/c5a1d753a08edd9435fab6d51bf5e629.poster.avif?t=1768507899\" width=1170 height=462 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307610/extras/c5a1d753a08edd9435fab6d51bf5e629.webm?t=1768507899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >挥杆前的宁静</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索精美设计、以物理为基础的球场，每一个弯道和障碍都在挑战你的瞄准。<br>在每场比赛前选择你疯狂的强化道具组合 — 从加速、护盾到更多选项 — 准备迎接终极高尔夫对决。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307610/extras/c8d5ad3a8f505f907e67a2173246c314.poster.avif?t=1768507899\" width=1170 height=748 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307610/extras/c8d5ad3a8f505f907e67a2173246c314.webm?t=1768507899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏌️ 主要特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 最多12名玩家在混乱的线上对战中竞争<br>• 基于物理的高尔夫战斗，真实碰撞与创意击球<br>• 可放置物品 — 坡道、反弹器及更多，可直接放置于球场<br>• 动态强化道具，彻底改变每场比赛的流程<br>• 回合制或实时游戏模式 — 自行选择混乱节奏<br>• 可自定义游戏规则 — 设置球洞数量、碰撞方式、队伍模式及操作方式（经典或鼠标挥杆）<br>• 快速、充满动作的回合，适合短时间游玩或深度竞技<br>• 持续更新，加入新物品、新模式及平衡调整</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >准备迎接混乱吗？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造球场、击球，并在实时高尔夫对战中战胜所有对手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最多十二名玩家、无限技巧、不间断的乐趣 — 欢迎来到 <strong>Ultimate Golf Battle</strong>。</p>",
